#eNCA speaks to Limpopo Transport Department spokesperson, Tidimalo Chuene. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - 16 people have died in an accident between a taxi and a truck near Groblersdal, Limpopo. The taxi was allegedly attempting to overtake when it hit the truck head-on. A second taxi was also damaged in the crash. READ: No answers for families devastated by Limpopo horror crash It's believed one of the taxis was carrying pupils to school. A second crash on the R71 near Ga-Makanye this morning left three people dead.